document_data.name: Yngukulub
document_data.mainbody: '''Yngukulub the Devourer''' was an [[aboleth]] ally of [[Gar Shatterkeel]] at the [[Fane of the Eye]] under [[Tyar-Besil]] during the [[Elemental Evil]] crisis.
document_data.Personality: Yngukulub obeyed Gar because it believed that in the new era of [[Olhydra]] the aboleth would rule the world.
document_data.History: In [[1491 DR]], Yngukulub stayed at the Fane, served by a retinue of deranged [[kuo-toa]], until some adventurers infiltrated the temple and killed it.
